description: The recommendations are based on a six-card deck with rules found in most American casinos.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Basic Strategy what should eleven do against dealer ten
Alexa, ask Basic Strategy what should soft seventeen do against a three
Alexa, ask Basic Strategy what should a pair of fours do on a dealer six
name: Blackjack Basic Strategy
shortDescription: Provides a recommendation for a Blackjack hand based on Basic Strategy ("the book").
